{"tid":972224,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩作品內容同畫風/書名/第一印象好大反差?","createTime":"2019-01-07T08:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T13:19:54.000Z","uid":197873,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7a501daec4355da50f3f9b22fbef67c76f47ec","tid":972224,"uid":197873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"如題,啱啱睇完曬<del>顏藝</del>遊戲三人娘想搵野睇<br />\n下面3個當時唔知講咩就咁見到封面就拎黎睇,所以印象好深<br />\n<br />\n來自深淵: 最近開始講生駭村點黎真係越諗越不安,仲話溫馨治癒果D係咪祈手黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得唯一治癒點只有娜娜奇嘅毛毛觸感 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星星公主&amp;地球防衛少年:<br />\n其實呢兩個中文譯名真係好令人誤會...<br />\n不過就咁睇封面同簡介真係會以為係溫馨奇幻同熱血少年漫畫<br />\n睇完我只想講:鬼頭莫宏我dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得以前係K島有個人唔知頭唔知路買左成set星星公主俾個讀小學嘅侄女,俾人斷撚曬六親都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星星公主睇完想搵Man in black洗腦,不過地球防衛少年雖然胃痛但其實好好睇我幾鍾意<br />\n有種絕望中有少少光明嘅感覺?唔知點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10d832eec3f99f9a67c9540169879b7c6e39e93","tid":972224,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"What I watched: 刀使 <br />\nWhat I exptected: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWhat I got: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWhat I watched: Kemono Friends <br />\nWhat I exptected: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWhat I got: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWhat I watched: High School Fleet <br />\nWhat I exptected: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWhat I got: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as